
Core Commands (10):
1. /menu or /start - Main command menu with inline buttons
2. /trade - Trading operations menu
3. /account - Account information menu
4. /settings - Bot configuration menu
5. /stats - Trading statistics menu
6. /charts - Chart visualization menu
7. /power - Toggle trading on/off
8. /status - Display current bot status
9. /help - Show help information
10. /admin - Admin commands menu
